[Running environment]

 AMIGA computer and joystick is necessary.
 Recommend high-speed CPU.

[How to start]

 First of all, copy medplayer.library in libs.
 Next, copy gnysht.font and gnysht drawer in fonts.
 Afterward, double Click "GonyShoot" icon to start the game.

[Rules of this game]

 GonyShoot is simple shooting game.
 Destroy enemies one and all, and dodge enemies and shells.

 After Ver1.35, attack method exists 3 kinds:
  1, Main shot

   Several bullets are fired in continuation automatically when push a button once.
   According to body and distance with an enemy, a score provided changes.

  2, All-Range Laser

   When continue pushing a button, energy is accumulated.
   And, When releasing button, All-Range Laser is fired.
   During discharge, you can control a direction of laser to backside of player's movement direction.
   High score is provided by destroying enemies in continuation.

  3, Backfire

   If you move ship to ahead, backfire is appeared.
   You can attack to enemies by backfire.
   20 times of usual score is provided. 
   Try this!

 After Ver1.20, difficulty rises by a score.

 After Ver1.50, the time attack mode exists.

  You compete times that getting 1000000 points.
  At the this mode, enemy's appearance pattern is fixed.
  And, the number that an enemy appears is little, too.
  Therefore, this mode can be recommend to beginners too.

